search_results.title: Laurie Nelson
search_results.snippet: Laurie Nelson is a native of Northern Virginia, just outside of Washington DC, where she is both a voice teacher and an award-winning oil painter.

search_results.title: Pre-Health Advisor Laurie Nelson Retires after 50 Years at ...
search_results.snippet: Laurie Nelson worked as an assistant professor of Physical Education and the pre-health adviser at Pepperdine for five decades and will retire this spring.
